<hr data-start="244" data-end="247">
<h2 data-section-id="lzfes8" data-start="249" data-end="314"><span role="text"><strong data-start="252" data-end="314">Website Structure &amp; Content for Superior MRI Services Inc.</strong></span></h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1p76d39" data-start="316" data-end="335"><span role="text"><strong data-start="320" data-end="335">1. Homepage</strong></span></h3>
<p data-start="337" data-end="356"><strong data-start="337" data-end="354">Hero Section:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="357" data-end="690">
<li data-section-id="1tcwiss" data-start="357" data-end="420">
<p data-start="359" data-end="420">Headline: <em data-start="369" data-end="418">“High-Quality Mobile Imaging, Wherever You Are”</em></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="152789k" data-start="421" data-end="537">
<p data-start="423" data-end="537">Subheadline: <em data-start="436" data-end="535">“Serving Mississippi and the Southeast with convenient, patient-focused MRI services since 2011.”</em></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1sh4aag" data-start="538" data-end="609">
<p data-start="540" data-end="609">Call-to-Action Buttons: <em data-start="564" data-end="591">“Schedule an Appointment”</em>, <em data-start="593" data-end="607">“Learn More”</em></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="jpe4jl" data-start="610" data-end="690">
<p data-start="612" data-end="690">Background: Image of a mobile MRI van or patient-friendly imaging environment.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="692" data-end="728"><strong data-start="692" data-end="726">About Section (short version):</strong></p>
<ul data-start="729" data-end="979">
<li data-section-id="e1jeck" data-start="729" data-end="940">
<p data-start="731" data-end="940"><em data-start="731" data-end="938">“Superior MRI Services Inc. has been providing mobile imaging solutions across Mississippi and the Southeast since 2011. Our 24 locations prioritize patient comfort, convenience, and high-quality results.”</em></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10vxd70" data-start="941" data-end="979">
<p data-start="943" data-end="979"><em data-start="943" data-end="979">“Learn More” → Links to About Page</em></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="981" data-end="1004"><strong data-start="981" data-end="1002">Services Section:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1005" data-end="1177">
<li data-section-id="qcgrw2" data-start="1005" data-end="1018">
<p data-start="1007" data-end="1018">MRI Scans</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1rqezs1" data-start="1019" data-end="1061">
<p data-start="1021" data-end="1061">Mobile Imaging for Clinics &amp; Hospitals</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="kdxjs7" data-start="1062" data-end="1119">
<p data-start="1064" data-end="1119">Specialized Imaging Services (e.g., open MRI, 3T MRI)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="rlkyf" data-start="1120" data-end="1177">
<p data-start="1122" data-end="1177">Each service with a short description + icon or image</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1179" data-end="1207"><strong data-start="1179" data-end="1205">Why Choose Us Section:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1208" data-end="1331">
<li data-section-id="18kfdft" data-start="1208" data-end="1235">
<p data-start="1210" data-end="1235">24 Convenient Locations</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="az9jc3" data-start="1236" data-end="1266">
<p data-start="1238" data-end="1266">Experienced Radiology Team</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1pl24l5" data-start="1267" data-end="1302">
