><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"card"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;h3&gt;</span><span>MRI Scans</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/h3&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;p&gt;</span><span>Comprehensive MRI imaging with advanced equipment.</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"card"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;h3&gt;</span><span>Mobile Imaging</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/h3&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;p&gt;</span><span>We bring imaging directly to clinics, hospitals, and patient homes.</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"card"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;h3&gt;</span><span>Specialized Imaging</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/h3&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;p&gt;</span><span>Open MRI, 3T MRI, and other advanced techniques for precise diagnostics.</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/section&gt;</span><br><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼl">&lt;!-- Contact CTA --&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;section</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">id</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"contact"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"contact-cta"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼv">