idth:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="6ab31035-ae3a-43e6-9397-1fc3ae7436af" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-mini" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="173">Perfect! I’ll create a <strong data-start="23" data-end="73">modern, professional, fully responsive website</strong> for <strong data-start="78" data-end="108">Superior MRI Services Inc.</strong> that’s ready to upload to <strong data-start="135" data-end="145">GitHub</strong> and deploy on <strong data-start="160" data-end="170">Vercel</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="175" data-end="201">This version will include:</p>
<ul data-start="203" data-end="450">
<li data-section-id="1xuvq8v" data-start="203" data-end="250">
<p data-start="205" data-end="250">Modern hero section with background and CTA</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1prttd3" data-start="251" data-end="279">
<p data-start="253" data-end="279">Clean, responsive layout</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1llgx8h" data-start="280" data-end="317">
<p data-start="282" data-end="317">Services cards with hover effects</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1g0vazf" data-start="318" data-end="359">
<p data-start="320" data-end="359">About section with milestone timeline</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="fqlw0e" data-start="360" data-end="404">
<p data-start="362" data-end="404">Locations page with map and contact info</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1t83cwu" data-start="405" data-end="421">
<p data-start="407" data-end="421">Contact form</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ge6qpd" data-start="422" data-end="450">
<p data-start="424" data-end="450">Sticky navbar and footer</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="452" data-end="516">Here’s the <strong data-start="463" data-end="502">complete folder structure with code</strong> ready to use:</p>
<hr data-start="518" data-end="521">
<h2 data-section-id="4wr7om" data-start="523" data-end="546"><span role="text"><strong data-start="526" data-end="546">Folder Structure</strong></span></h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="548" data-end="781"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>superior-mri-website/</span><br><span>├─ index.html</span><br><span>├─ about.html</span><br><span>├─ services.html</span><br><span>├─ locations.html</span><br><span>├─ contact.html</span><br><span>├─ styles.css</span><br><span>└─ images/</span><br><span>     ├─ hero.jpg</span><br><span>     ├─ mobile-mri.jpg</span><br><span>     ├─ staff.jpg</span><br><span>     └─ icons/ (MRI, mobile, specialized)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="783" data-end="786">
<h2 data-section-id="d1cs5b" data-start="788" data-end="825"><span role="text"><strong data-start="791" data-end="808">1. styles.css</strong> (modern styling)</span></h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="827" data-end="3648"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼl">/* Global Styles */</span><br><span class="ͼn">*</span><span> {</span><br><span>    margin: </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>    padding: </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>    box-sizing: </span><span class="ͼq">border-box</span><span>;</span><br><span>    font-family: </span><span class="ͼr">'Roboto'</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">sans-serif</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">body</span><span> {</span><br><span>    line-height: </span><span class="ͼq">1.6</span><span>;</span><br><span>    color: #1F2937;</span><br><span>    background-color: #F3F4F6;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* Navbar */</span><br><span class="ͼv">nav</span><span> {</span><br><span>    background-color: #1E3A8A;</span><br><span>    color: </span><span class="ͼq">white</span><span>;</span><br><span>    display: </span><span class="ͼq">flex</span><span>;</span><br><span>    justify-content: </span><span class="ͼq">space-between</span><span>;</span><br><span>    align-items: </span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>    padding: </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">rem</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">2</span><span class="ͼn">rem</span><span>;</span><br><span>    position: </span><span class="ͼq">sticky</span><span>;</span><br><span>    top: </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>    z-index: </span><span class="ͼq">1000</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">nav</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">a</span><span> {</span><br><span>    color: </span><span class="ͼq">white</span><span>;</span><br><span>    text-decoration: </span><span class="ͼq">none</span><span>;</span><br><span>    margin-left: </span><span class="ͼq">1.5</span><span class="ͼn">rem</span><span>;</span><br><span>    font-weight: </span><span class="ͼq">500</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">nav</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">a</span><span>:</span><span class="ͼs">hover</span><span> {</span><br><span>    color: #FACC15;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* Hero Section */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero</span><span> {</span><br><span>    background: </span><span class="ͼq">url</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">'images/hero.jpg'</span><span>) </span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span class="ͼn">/</span><span class="ͼq">cover</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">no-repeat</span><span>;</span><br><span>    height: </span><span class="ͼq">80</span><span class="ͼn">vh</span><span>;</span><br><span>    display: </span><span class="ͼq">flex</span><span>;</span><br><span>    flex-direction: </span><span class="ͼq">column</span><span>;</span><br><span>    justify-content: </span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>    align-items: </span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>    text-align: </span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>    color: </span><span class="ͼq">white</span><span>;</span><br><span>    padding: </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">rem</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">h1</span><span> {</span><br><span>    font-size: </span><span class="ͼq">3</span><span class="ͼn">rem</span><span>;</span><br><span>    font-weight: </span><span class="ͼq">700</span><span>;</span><br><span>    margin-bottom: </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">rem</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">p</span><span> {</span><br><span>    font-size: </span><span class="ͼq">1.5</span><span class="ͼn">rem</span><span>;</span><br><span>    margin-bottom: </span><span class="ͼq">2</span><span class="ͼn">rem</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">a</span><span> {</span><br><span>    background-color: #FACC15;</span><br><span>    color: #1E3A8A;</span><br><span>    padding: </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">rem</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">2</span><span class="ͼn">rem</span><span>;</span><br><span>    border-radius: </span><span class="ͼq">0.5</span><span class="ͼn">rem</span><span>;</span><br><span>    font-weight: </span><span class="ͼq">600</span><span>;</span><br><span>    text-decoration: </span><span class="ͼq">none</span><span>;</span><br><span>    transition: </span><span class="ͼq">background</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0.3</span><span class="ͼn">s</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">a</span><span>:</span><span class="ͼs">hover</span><span> {</span><br><span>    background-color: #EAB308;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* Section Titles */</span><br><span class="ͼv">section</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">h2</span><span> {</span><br><span>    text-align: </span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>    font-size: </span><span class="ͼq">2.5</span><span class="ͼn">rem</span><span>;</span><br><span>    margin-bottom: </span><span class="ͼq">2</span><span class="ͼn">rem</span><span>;</span><br><span>    color: #1E3A8A;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* Services Section */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">services</span><span> {</span><br><span>    display: </span><span class="ͼq">grid</span><span>;</span><br><span>    grid-template-columns: </span><span class="ͼn">repeat</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">auto-fit</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼn">minmax</span><span>(</span><