s="ͼu">href</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"services.html"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><span>Services</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;a</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">href</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"locations.html"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><span>Locations</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;a</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">href</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"contact.html"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><span>Contact</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/nav&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;section&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;h2&gt;</span><span>Contact Us</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/h2&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;p&gt;</span><span>Fill out the form below or call us at </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;strong&gt;</span><span>662-299-0582</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/strong&gt;</span><span> or email </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;strong&gt;</span><span>Shaun@superiormri.com</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/strong&gt;</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;form</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"contact-form"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;input</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">type</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"text"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">placeholder</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"Your Name"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">required</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;input</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">type</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"email"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">placeholder</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"Email Address"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">required</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;input</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">type</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"tel"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">placeholder</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"Phone Number"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;textarea</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">rows</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"5"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">placeholder</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"Message"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;button</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">type</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"submit"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><span>Submit</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/button&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/form&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/section&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;footer&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼr">&amp;copy;</span><span> 2026 Superior MRI Services Inc.</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/footer&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/body&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/html&gt;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="7412" data-end="7415">
<p data-start="7417" data-end="7433">✅ <strong data-start="7419" data-end="7433">Next Steps</strong></p>
<ol data-start="7435" data-end="7888">
<li data-section-id="n8h14b" data-start="7435" data-end="7503">
<p data-start="7438" data-end="7503">Create a folder on your computer called <code data-start="7478" data-end="7500">superior-mri-website</code>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1o8dq9t" data-start="7504" data-end="7623">
<p data-start="7507" data-end="7623">Add the files above (<code data-start="7528" data-end="7540">index.html</code>, <code data-start="7542" data-end="7554">about.html</code>, <code data-start="7556" data-end="7571">services.html</code>, <code data-start="7573" data-end="7589">locations.html</code>, <code data-start="7591" data-end="7605">contact.html</code>, <code data-start="7607" data-end="7619">styles.css</code>).</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1wrv910" data-start="7624" data-end="7723">
<p data-start="7627" data-end="7723">Add images to the <code data-start="7645" data-end="7654">images/</code> folder. You can use free stock photos for MRI, clinics, and staff.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="76ii1t" data-start="7724" data-end="7781">
<p data-start="7727" data-end="7781">Upload the entire folder to a <strong data-start="7757" data-end="7778">GitHub repository</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1u3o98a" data-start="7782" data-end="7888">
<p data-start="7785" data-end="7888">Go to <strong data-start="7791" data-end="7801">Vercel</strong>, click <strong data-start="7809" data-end="7854">New Project → Import GitHub Repo → Deploy</strong>, and your website will be live.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="7890" data-end="7893">
<p data-start="7895" data-end="8079">If you want, I can <strong data-start="7914" data-end="7965">also make the folder ready-to-download as a ZIP</strong>, with placeholder images and icons, so you literally just upload it to GitHub and deploy—no extra setup needed.</p>
<p data-start="8081" data-end="8107" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Do you want me to do that?</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pre