<hr data-start="172" data-end="175">
<h2 data-section-id="1ot3aih" data-start="177" data-end="203"><span role="text"><strong data-start="180" data-end="203">1. Folder Structure</strong></span></h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="205" data-end="670"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>superior-mri-website/</span><br><span>├─ index.html</span><br><span>├─ about.html</span><br><span>├─ services.html</span><br><span>├─ locations.html</span><br><span>├─ contact.html</span><br><span>├─ styles.css</span><br><span>└─ images/</span><br><span>     ├─ hero.jpg           (placeholder link below)</span><br><span>     ├─ mobile-mri.jpg     (placeholder link below)</span><br><span>     ├─ staff.jpg          (placeholder link below)</span><br><span>     └─ icons/</span><br><span>         ├─ mri.png        (placeholder link below)</span><br><span>         ├─ mobile.png     (placeholder link below)</span><br><span>         └─ specialized.png (placeholder link below)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="672" data-end="675">
<h2 data-section-id="1kpmibp" data-start="677" data-end="720"><span role="text"><strong data-start="680" data-end="720">2. Placeholder Images &amp; Icons (Free)</strong></span></h2>
<p data-start="722" data-end="789">You can download these images and save them in the <code data-start="773" data-end="781">images</code> folder:</p>
<ul data-start="791" data-end="1575">
<li data-section-id="1bndre7" data-start="791" data-end="919">
<p data-start="793" data-end="919"><strong data-start="793" data-end="818">Hero Image (hero.jpg)</strong> – Mobile MRI:<br data-start="832" data-end="835">
<a data-start="837" data-end="919" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://unsplash.com/photos/jEbnKxR1bXY<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1eqfpy1" data-start="921" data-end="1046">
<p data-start="923" data-end="1046"><strong data-start="923" data-end="958">Mobile MRI Van (mobile-mri.jpg)</strong>:<br data-start="959" data-end="962">
<a data-start="964" data-end="1046" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://unsplash.com/photos/URpOJ_RKqHs<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cz8s48" data-start="1048" data-end="1175">
<p data-start="1050" data-end="1175"><strong data-start="1050" data-end="1087">Staff / Friendly Team (staff.jpg)</strong>:<br data-start="1088" data-end="1091">
<a data-start="1093" data-end="1175" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://unsplash.com/photos/Oalh2MojUuk<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="acetv6" data-start="1177" data-end="1575">
<p data-start="1179" data-end="1226"><strong data-start="1179" data-end="1188">Icons</strong> (use free PNGs or emoji-style icons):</p>
<ul data-start="1229" data-end="1575">
<li data-section-id="15z44g3" data-start="1229" data-end="1332">
<p data-start="1231" data-end="1332">MRI: <a data-start="1236" data-end="1332" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/mri_1584710<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1unzg5x" data-start="1335" data-end="1453">
<p data-start="1337" data-end="1453">Mobile: <a data-start="1345" data-end="1453" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/ambulance_1684187<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1t79mrq" data-start="1456" data-end="1575">
<p data-start="1458" data-end="1575">Specialized: <a data-start="1471" data-end="1575" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link cursor-pointer">https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/hospital_685066<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<blockquote data-start="1577" data-end="1666">
<p data-start="1579" data-end="1666">Save icons in <code data-start="1593" data-end="1608">images/icons/</code> and name them <code data-start="1623" data-end="1632">mri.png</code>, <code data-start="1634" data-end="1646">mobile.png</code>, <code data-start="1648" data-end="1665">specialized.png</code>.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="1668" data-end="1671">
<h2 data-section-id="p79xc0" data-start="1673" data-end="1701"><span role="text"><strong data-start="1676" data-end="1701">3. Ready-to-Copy Code</strong></span></h2>
<ul data-start="1703" data-end="1933">
<li data-section-id="199qd61" data-start="1703" data-end="1822">
<p data-start="1705" data-end="1822">Use the <strong data-start="1713" data-end="1819">HTML code I provided for <code data-start="1740" data-end="1752">index.html</code>, <code data-start="1754" data-end="1766">about.html</code>, <code data-start="1768" data-end="1783">services.html</code>, <code data-start="1785" data-end="1801">locations.html</code>, <code data-start="1803" data-end="1817">contact.html</code></strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11crfy4" data-start="1823" data-end="1864">
<p data-start="1825" data-end="1864">Use the <strong data-start="1833" data-end="1861">CSS code in <code data-start="1847" data-end="1859">styles.css</code></strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1c057x1" data-start="1865" data-end="1933">
<p data-start="1867" data-end="1933">The image paths in the HTML already match this folder structure.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1935" data-end="1938">
<h2 data-section-id="5lkixt" data-start="1940" data-end="1975"><span role="text"><strong data-start="1943" data-end="1975">4. Create the ZIP and Deploy</strong></span></h2>
<ol data-start="1977" data-end="2393">
<li data-section-id="1t88qyq" data-start="1977" data-end="2037">
<p data-start="1980" data-end="2037"><strong data-start="1980" data-end="2011">Create the folder structure</strong> above on your computer.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="3abj0k" data-start="2038" data-end="2087">
<p data-start="2041" data-end="2087"><strong data-start="2041" data-end="2068">Copy all HTML/CSS files</strong> into the folder.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="mdvdfv" data-start="2088" data-end="2147">
<p data-start="2091" data-end="2147"><strong data-start="2091" data-end="2130">Download and place the images/icons</strong> as instructed.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="p6n5te" data-start="2148" data-end="2217">
<p data-start="2151" data-end="2217"><strong data-start="2151" data-end="2174">Compress the folder</strong> into a ZIP (<code data-start="2187" data-end="2213">superior-mri-website.zip</code>).</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="jusldu" data-start="2218" data-end="2301">
<p data-start="2221" data-end="2244"><strong data-start="2221" data-end="2241">Upload to GitHub</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="2248" data-end="2301">
<li data-section-id="95l3ck" data-start="2248" data-end="2301">
<p data-start="2250" data-end="2301">Create a new repository → drag &amp; drop your files.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="v7apef" data-start="2302" data-end="2393">
<p data-start="2305" data-end="2328"><strong data-start="2305" data-end="2325">Deploy on Vercel</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="2332" data-end="2393">
<li data-section-id="114zuri" data-start="2332" data-end="2393">
<p data-start="2334" data-end="2393">Go to Vercel → New Project → Import GitHub repo → Deploy.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<blockquote data-start="2395" data-end="2506">
<p data-start="2397" data-end="2506">Your website will be live with <strong data-start="2428" data-end="2503">responsive layout, professional look, and ready for patients or clinics</strong>.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="2508" data-end="2511">
<p data-start="2513" data-end="2685">If you want, I can <strong data-start="2532" data-end="2614">also make a visual “mockup” of how the homepage and services section will look</strong> with these images, so you can see the final design before uploading.</p>
<p data-start="2687" data-end="2713" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Do you want me to do that?</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pre