<p data-start="130" data-end="252">Here it is 👇<br data-start="143" data-end="146">
<span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" title="Download your MRI truck image" type="button">Download your MRI truck image</button></span></p>
<hr data-start="254" data-end="257">
<h2 data-section-id="13qr91j" data-start="259" data-end="303"><span role="text"><strong data-start="262" data-end="303">How to Use This Image on Your Website</strong></span></h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1vx1o97" data-start="305" data-end="329"><span role="text"><strong data-start="309" data-end="329">Step 1: Download</strong></span></h3>
<ul data-start="330" data-end="417">
<li data-section-id="aprhje" data-start="330" data-end="361">
<p data-start="332" data-end="361">Right-click the image above</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="dp991" data-start="362" data-end="392">
<p data-start="364" data-end="392">Click <strong data-start="370" data-end="390">“Save image as…”</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fkgpdr" data-start="393" data-end="417">
<p data-start="395" data-end="417">Save it as: <code data-start="407" data-end="417">hero.jpg</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="419" data-end="422">
<h3 data-section-id="7jac6y" data-start="424" data-end="466"><span role="text"><strong data-start="428" data-end="466">Step 2: Add to Your Website Folder</strong></span></h3>
<p data-start="467" data-end="479">Put it here:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="480" data-end="524"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>superior-mri-website/images/hero.jpg</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="526" data-end="529">
<h3 data-section-id="1nxi7pb" data-start="531" data-end="577"><span role="text"><strong data-start="535" data-end="577">Step 3: Already Connected in Your Code</strong></span></h3>
<p data-start="578" data-end="605">Your homepage already uses:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="606" data-end="689"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-lbtco6v1.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero</span><span> {</span><br><span>    background: </span><span class="ͼq">url</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">'images/hero.jpg'</span><span>) </span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span class="ͼn">/</span><span class="ͼq">cover</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">no-repeat</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="691" data-end="768">So once you drop the file in, <strong data-start="721" data-end="767">it will automatically show up on your site</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="770" data-end="773">
<h2 data-section-id="j5sew2" data-start="775" data-end="801"><span role="text"><strong data-start="778" data-end="801">Pro Tip (Important)</strong></span></h2>
<p data-start="802" data-end="954">This image looks great, but for a real business like <strong data-start="855" data-end="871">Superior MRI</strong>, you’ll get <em data-start="884" data-end="919">much better trust and conversions</em> if you eventually replace it with:</p>
<ul data-start="956" data-end="1027">
<li data-section-id="6et6x6" data-start="956" data-end="992">
<p data-start="958" data-end="992">A <strong data-start="960" data-end="992">real photo of your MRI truck</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="pk8ub4" data-start="993" data-end="1027">
<p data-start="995" data-end="1027">Or a branded unit with your logo</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1029" data-end="1091">Even hospitals and clinics expect to see the actual equipment.</p>
<hr data-start="1093" data-end="1096">
<h2 data-section-id="oagflm" data-start="1098" data-end="1129"><span role="text"><strong data-start="1101" data-end="1129">Want Next-Level Upgrade?</strong></span></h2>
<p data-start="1130" data-end="1141">I can also:</p>
<ul data-start="1142" data-end="1309">
<li data-section-id="9t4bez" data-start="1142" data-end="1190">
<p data-start="1144" data-end="1190">Add your <strong data-start="1153" data-end="1190">company logo onto the truck image</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1p4vio7" data-start="1191" data-end="1252">
<p data-start="1193" data-end="1252">Make it look <strong data-start="1206" data-end="1252">branded with “Superior MRI” on the trailer</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1lt6hy3" data-start="1253" data-end="1309">
<p data-start="1255" data-end="1309">Or create <strong data-start="1265" data-end="1309">multiple hero images for different pages</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1311" data-end="1326">Just tell me 👍</p>
